    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) is an Internet protocol for accessing distributed directory services that act in accordance with X.500 data and service models.  This document provides a road map of the LDAP Technical Specification. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
